BUT

body:
Since I moved I’ve been trying to make new friends down here (which is hard when you have crippling social anxiety lol)

BUT

I met up with this dude I met on Bumble last night and I was super nervous and then when we were talking he was like “can I just say Taylor Swift was totally cheated for the Grammy nominations this year. Delicate alone deserved at least 3 nominations not to mention the masterpiece that is Reputation itself” and I was like Oh We Are Gonna Be Friends.

blog.title: Victoria❤️Taylor
blog.description:
A Chinese Girl 
Dreaming about singing i did Something bad With my Queen

body:
Day 10💔

Dear Taylor,

I am little sad today,because i think nobody really cares about me and nobody will see my efforts,people always like pushing others to do something they dont want to,and take advantage of it,then leave…How could they do this??

I always choose to be positive and trust people,but why they always make me disappointed and make my world collide because of them?💔

I really wanna do something bad but i cant,because you always tell us to be kind and to be generous….I guess i really need some time to recover from this bad thing….

Well,good night Taylor❤️I love you❤️

@taylorswift @taylornation
